org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.extensionpoints

Class MethodInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.extensionpoints.MethodInfo

  • public class MethodInfo
extends Object
    Additional information about a method that has been generated for a UML behavior. This information is used by the CDT editor integration to locate the method in the code, but might be useful for other languages as well.
